description: AWS IoT Client for the AWS SDK for C++. AWS SDK for C++ provides a modern C++ (version C++ 11 or later) interface for Amazon Web Services (AWS). It is meant to be performant and fully functioning with low- and high-level SDKs, while minimizing dependencies and providing platform portability (Windows, OSX, Linux, and mobile).
releaseNotes: Summary of changes made in this release of the package.
summary: v120 and v140 binary packages along with header files. No custom memory management. Standard Compiler flags used. For more info, see https://github.com/aws/aws-sdk-cpp/blob/master/README.md
title: AWS SDK for C++ (AWS IoT)
